        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-b3ff0a6b-af5d-48fb-95f5-71c64623e345">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-b3ff0a6b-af5d-48fb-95f5-71c64623e345">
                Mr. Lansbury
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b3ff0a6b-af5d-48fb-95f5-71c64623e345" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-12-06/debates/67830417-a992-4e78-a2cf-671eb839ac2a/NationalVoluntaryService#contribution-b3ff0a6b-af5d-48fb-95f5-71c64623e345">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I inquire of the right hon. Gentleman whether these committees will advise people to leave certain occupations and join or consider joining the Territorial or the Regular Services?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b3ff0a6b-af5d-48fb-95f5-71c64623e345" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-12-06/debates/67830417-a992-4e78-a2cf-671eb839ac2a/NationalVoluntaryService#contribution-b3ff0a6b-af5d-48fb-95f5-71c64623e345">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4">
                Sir J. Anderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-12-06/debates/67830417-a992-4e78-a2cf-671eb839ac2a/NationalVoluntaryService#contribution-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I should say not, so far as leaving occupations is concerned. The object is to provide the best possible guidance for people who wish to volunteer for work of national importance.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-12-06/debates/67830417-a992-4e78-a2cf-671eb839ac2a/NationalVoluntaryService#contribution-09ae6bc2-55a2-47d2-807d-fe93c5eec8e4">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-f25c8f08-4b7c-4d64-80d7-db072b84f687">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-f25c8f08-4b7c-4d64-80d7-db072b84f687">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
