<p class="">If the right hon. Gentleman makes his point in a speech or lets me know otherwise what it is, I will do my best to deal with it.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0db7ec7c-f659-42e6-bf0b-a1d7a1b9ae44" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
