        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">What checks will be imposed upon these special registers? Is there not a danger that certain people will get themselves classified, particularly in the second category, and thereby escape military service in the event of war?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-de921da5-c91f-458d-bec5-1f654857148b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-12-06/debates/67830417-a992-4e78-a2cf-671eb839ac2a/NationalVoluntaryService#contribution-de921da5-c91f-458d-bec5-1f654857148b">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
