<p class="">After completion of the form the compulsion would cease?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-78a773e0-5b85-4426-963f-611554b83c4b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
