            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-e69be534-f065-4daa-a3b6-3b8c6e371a8f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
