            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6f0e62d3-dc33-47fe-bc82-fba556dc2057">
                Mr. Hopkinson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6f0e62d3-dc33-47fe-bc82-fba556dc2057" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-12-06/debates/67830417-a992-4e78-a2cf-671eb839ac2a/NationalVoluntaryService#contribution-6f0e62d3-dc33-47fe-bc82-fba556dc2057">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Let us get this point clear. It is not a question of what the Army, the Navy or any Department thinks. It is a question of the fundamental right of the citizen to serve in the armed forces.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6f0e62d3-dc33-47fe-bc82-fba556dc2057" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-12-06/debates/67830417-a992-4e78-a2cf-671eb839ac2a/NationalVoluntaryService#contribution-6f0e62d3-dc33-47fe-bc82-fba556dc2057">
